t: Amazon Leaffish (Monocirrhus polyacanthus) | Better Know a Fish!
s: April 12, 2015 - Another fabulous fish species I got to see up close at the California Academy of Sciences during my visit last Thursday was the Amazon leaffish (Monocirrhus polyacanthus).
